---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Seller AI HQ, practical AI tools and workflows for online sellers"
  description="Curated AI tools, tested workflows, and practical guides for marketplace sellers, small ecommerce brands, and product creators."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="pill">Built for ecommerce sellers, creators, and marketplace operators</div>
        <h1>Use AI to sell better, faster, and with less wasted motion.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Seller AI HQ helps product-based businesses find useful AI tools for listings, visuals, content, and growth.
          No bloated directory. No fake hype. Just practical stack decisions.
        </p>
        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="btn primary" href="/tools">Browse tool categories</a>
          <a class="btn secondary" href="/guides">Read starter guides</a>
        </div>
        <div class="accent-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="pill">Early positioning</div>
        <div class="feature-list">
          <div class="feature">
            <strong>Curated tool stack</strong>
            <span class="mini">We focus on tools sellers can actually use for listings, images, and content workflows.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <strong>Search-first content</strong>
            <span class="mini">The site is being built around high-intent pages that can attract organic traffic and future affiliate revenue.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <strong>Future AI advisor layer</strong>
            <span class="mini">Later, this becomes a smarter recommendation engine, not just a static content site.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="trust">
      <div class="card"><strong>Live domain</strong><div class="mini">selleraihq.com is active and deployed.</div></div>
      <div class="card"><strong>Brand handle secured</strong><div class="mini">@selleraihq is already taken and aligned.</div></div>
      <div class="card"><strong>SEO structure started</strong><div class="mini">Core pages and content lanes are already in place.</div></div>
      <div class="card"><strong>Built to expand</strong><div class="mini">The brand can scale beyond one marketplace.</div></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="tools">
    <h2>Start with the three highest-value categories</h2>
    <p class="top">These are the categories most likely to matter to sellers early and convert into monetizable interest later.</p>
    <div class="grid-3">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="pill">Listings</div>
        <h3>Copy and SEO</h3>
        <p class="mini">Title generators, description tools, keyword research, and listing optimization workflows.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="pill">Creative</div>
        <h3>Images and mockups</h3>
        <p class="mini">Product visuals, cleanup tools, mockup builders, scene generation, and image enhancement.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="pill">Growth</div>
        <h3>Content and marketing</h3>
        <p class="mini">Email helpers, post generation, short-form content workflows, and lightweight campaign support.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="guides">
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="pill">Money pages coming next</div>
        <h3>Pages that can actually make money</h3>
        <ul class="mini" style="padding-left:18px; margin: 12px 0 0;">
          <li>Best AI tools for sellers in 2026</li>
          <li>Best AI image tools for product sellers</li>
          <li>Best AI copy tools for listings and SEO</li>
          <li>Best low-cost AI stack for ecommerce sellers</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="pill">Authority layer</div>
        <h3>Guides that build trust</h3>
        <ul class="mini" style="padding-left:18px; margin: 12px 0 0;">
          <li>How to use AI for product listings without sounding robotic</li>
          <li>How to improve product visuals with AI</li>
          <li>How solo sellers can use AI without adding tool chaos</li>
          <li>What AI is actually worth paying for as a seller</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="stack">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="pill">Why this can work</div>
      <h2>This is being built as a lean, monetizable media asset.</h2>
      <p class="top">
        The short-term goal is simple, build a site that looks trustworthy enough to keep visitors, structured enough to rank,
        and focused enough to convert attention into affiliate clicks, partnerships, and later AI-assisted recommendations.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="btn primary" href="/about">Why this project exists</a>
        <a class="btn secondary" href="https://x.com/selleraihq" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Follow the build on X</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
